          <div class="text-4xl font-black text-[#F5521A] leading-none">8.9</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-[0.15em] font-black mt-2">Overall score</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-900 p-5 border-[3px] border-gray-800 relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-[#F5521A]/30 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="text-4xl font-black text-white leading-none">18h</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-[0.15em] font-black mt-2">Time spent</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-5 border-[3px] border-gray-200 relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-[#F5521A]/50 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 leading-none">2:47</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-[0.15em] font-black mt-2">AI generation</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#F5521A] p-5 border-[3px] border-[#D44A1A] relative overflow-hidden shadow-[0_4px_0_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)] group-hover:shadow-[0_6px_0_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.25)] group-hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="text-4xl font-black text-white leading-none">47</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-white/80 uppercase tracking-[0.15em] font-black mt-2">Pages generated</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- WHAT I TESTED - Social Proof Checklist -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-50 to-teal-100 border-[3px] border-teal-200 p-6 md:p-8 mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-teal-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900">What I Tested</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">18 hours of hands-on testing across 7 days</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-700"><strong>Sitemap generation</strong> (47-page SaaS site)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-700"><strong>Wireframe export</strong> to Framer</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-700"><strong>Figma export</strong> compatibility</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-700"><strong>Component library</strong> integration</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-700"><strong>Client presentation</strong> mode</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-700"><strong>Sitemap iteration</strong> and editing</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-700"><strong>E-commerce flows</strong> (basic)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-700"><strong>Free tier limits</strong> (3 projects)</span>
