								<a href={relumeUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="block w-full text-center px-4 py-3 border-[2px] border-teal-600 text-teal-600 font-black text-sm hover:bg-teal-600 hover:text-white transition-colors">Start Free</a>
